ve Development\\n- promote: Promote project-scoped instincts to global scope\\n- plan: Restate requirements, assess risks, and create step-by-step implementation\u2026\\n- sessions: Sessions Command\\n- evolve: Analyze instincts and suggest or generate evolved structures\\n- code-review: Code Review\\n- healthproxy: Proxy Health\\n- multi-execute: Execute - Multi-Model Collaborative Execution\\n- learn-eval: Extract reusable patterns from the session, self-evaluate quality before s\u2026\\n- go-review: Comprehensive Go code review for idiomatic patterns, concurrency safety, e\u2026\\n- instinct-status: Show learned instincts (project + global) with confidence\\n- tdd: Enforce test-driven development workflow. Scaffold interfaces, generate te\u2026\\n- deploy: Deploy Command\\n- checkpoint: Checkpoint Command\\n- refactor-clean: Refactor Clean\\n- projects: List known projects and their instinct statistics\\n- save-session: Save current session state to a dated file in ~/.claude/sessions/ so work \u2026\\n- update-docs: Update Documentation\\n- instinct-import: Import instincts from file or URL into project/global scope\\n- multi-agent: Multi-Agent Command\\n- build-fix: Build and Fix\\n- multi-frontend: Frontend - Frontend-Focused Development\\n- test-coverage: Test Coverage\\n- verify: Verification Command\\n- eval: Eval Command\\n- loop-status: Loop Status Command\\n- harness-audit: Harness Audit Command\\n- claw: Start NanoClaw v2 \u2014 ECC\\'s persistent, zero-dependency REPL with model rout\u2026\\n- setup: Project Setup\\n- loop-start: Loop Start Command\\n- e2e: Generate and run end-to-end tests with Playwright. Creates test journeys, \u2026\\n- voice: RAGS Voice Mode\\n- learn: /learn - Extract Reusable Patterns\\n- use-intelligence: use-intelligence\\n- instinct-export: Export instincts from project/global scope to a file\\n- proxy-status: Proxy Status\\n- quality-gate: Quality Gate Command\\n- telegram:access: Manage Telegram channel access \u2014 approve